      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">12.505</ph> Applicability of certain
laws to contracts for the acquisition of COTS items.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d734e8" class="- topic/p ">COTS items are a subset of commercial
items. Therefore, any laws listed in sections <xref href="12.503.dita#FAR_12_503"
                  base="i1112774"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">12.503</xref> and <xref href="12.504.dita#FAR_12_504"
                  base="i1112857"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">12.504</xref> are also inapplicable or
modified in their applicability to contracts or subcontracts for
the acquisition of COTS items. In addition, the following laws are
not applicable to contracts for the acquisition of COTS items:</p>
         <ol id="d713e28" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d740e18" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
               </p>
               <ol id="d713e38" class="- topic/ol ">
