                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d740e23">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        <ph rev="FAC 2021-04 January 19, 2021" class="- topic/ph ">The portion of <?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 12.505 by revising paragraph (a)?><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2019-016
?></ph>
